## ğŸ“ Changelog

### âœ¨ New Features
- **Role Replication**: Added support for replicating Kubernetes Roles across namespaces
- **RoleBinding Replication**: Added support for replicating Kubernetes RoleBindings across namespaces  
- **ServiceAccount Replication**: Added support for replicating Kubernetes ServiceAccounts across namespaces

### ğŸ› Bugfixes
- Fixed minor pipeline environment variable usages
- Fixed GitHub superlinter issues

### ğŸ”§ Improvements
- Moved kubebuilder annotations to individual replicator files for better organization
- Refactored controller structure and moved to root directory
- Improved codebase organization and structure
- Enhanced workflow permissions and security
- Upgraded GoLang version to 1.24.6
- Upgraded operator framework to v1.37.0
- Switched from CodeQL to Trivy for security scanning
- Improved build workflows and CI/CD processes

### ğŸ“š Documentation
